INSERT INTO testimonials (clientName, clientTitle, rating, testimonialText, serviceUsed, featured, approved, createdAt)
VALUES
('Nrupa Shah', NULL, 5, 'I was referred to Allresume Services. Great experience. Assisted me with my resume, cover letter and LinkedIn profile. Did an awesome job. Very happy with everything presented. Highly recommend Sonia and her team.', NULL, 1, 1, NOW()),
('Stewart McGrath', NULL, 5, 'Dear Sonia I hope this email finds you well. I wanted to take a moment to express my heartfelt gratitude for the fantastic resume and guidance you provided during my job search. I am excited to share that I have just accepted a position at SCE Group, and I couldn''t have done it without your help! Your expertise in showcasing my skills and experience truly made a difference. The feedback I received from interviewers was overwhelmingly positive, and I am confident your resume played a significant role in helping me stand out. Thank you once again for your professionalism, attention to detail, and for being such a wonderful support throughout this process. I will definitely recommend your services to anyone looking for resume assistance! Best regards, Nrupa Shah', NULL, 1, 1, NOW()),
('Martin Hill', NULL, 5, 'Thank you Sonia and team for the work completed on my professional resume, cover letter and LinkedIn profile. Highly skilled in understanding and then showcasing skills, attributes and strengths.', NULL, 1, 1, NOW()),
('Scott Green', NULL, 5, 'I have used All Resume Services for the first time about 5 years ago, the service I received was excellent! Very professional service! Within one week I scored an interview and was hired in two weeks! Recently I have changed careers and needed to update my resume and cover letter. Sonia and the team came to mind! I contacted Sonia, within no time I had a brand new and modern resume and cover letter. It''s amazing! - A year Ago', NULL, 1, 1, NOW()),
('Tony', NULL, 5, 'Thanks again for your services. I have received very positive feedback', NULL, 1, 1, NOW());
